    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl134_LabelType\">You have a passion for history and news concerning monastic disciplines.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl134_LabelType\">You gain a +1 trait bonus on checks with your choice of either Knowledge (local) or Knowledge (history), and the one you choose is always a class skill for you. In addition, you gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks made to gather information about any person with levels in monk.</span></p>",
